<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Bear Hide Boots Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
**Submitted by Teawine Turningleaf**<BR>
Updated by Balrak<BR>
<BR>
Just outside the Surefall Glade entrance you will find an NPC named Chanda Miller.<BR>
<BR>
If you approach her and tell her that "Baobob sent me" she will open up and talk to you.  Follow through the bracketted dialogue and you will find that she will make you a Bear Hide Belt for a low quality bear skin and 5gp.  For a medium quality bear skin and 15gp, she will make you the Bear Hide Boots, and for 21gp and a high quality bear skin she will make you a Bear Hide Cloak.<BR>
<BR>
You can obtain these skins in various zones where bears abound.  Such places as Qeynos Hills, all of the Karanas and the Commonlands are heavily populated with bears.<BR>
<BR>
You must use "skins" for this to work.  this has a tendency to confuse people who may be looking for "pelts".</div>
