<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Cooridaor</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-02 23:12:43</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>OK, here's the complete story...<BR>
<BR>
Chandra Miller sometimes sits by the fire with her husband Baobob, but sometimes she decides to go for a walk, usually along the right side wall from Surefall Glade. Hail her and tell her "Baobob sent me" (He'll tell you to do this if you talk to him first) She will tell you that she will make you a Bear Hide Belt for a Low Quality Bear Skin and 5gp; a pair of Bear Hide Boots for a Medium Quality Bear Skin and 15gp; or (if your faction with KaranaResidents is high enough) a Bear Hide Cloak for a High Quality Bear Skin and 21gp. You must give all gold. If you try to give the plat equivalent, she will thank you for your donation and go about her business... Baobob does a very similar business with Wolf Hide items, everything is the same, just substitute Wolf for Bear.<BR>
<BR>
Cooriador<BR>
Freeport Bard of Sixteen Songs<BR>
Druzzil-Ro</font></td></tr></table>
